Package: ImageFilterGroup5
Type: Package
Title: Filter a bitmap to grayscale or two-color image with a setting for cutoff
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Authors@R: 
    person("Eyvind", "Liljegren", , "eyvind.liljegren@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "NA"))
Maintainer: Eyvind Liljegren <eyvind.liljegren@gmail.com>   
Description: Provides functions for applying grayscale and two-color filtering to images,
             with an optional cutoff for the two-color effect.
